data.description: Just five years old and still looks new! Light, bright, beautiful and plenty of space for everyone! The primary suite is on the main floor, boasting a separate shower, garden tub and walk in closet with built in shelving. Another bedroom and full bath also on the main floor as well as the open kitchen, spacious living area and laundry room. Upstairs are the other two bedrooms and third full bath with a loft/bonus space in between. The back porch has been screened in for your enjoyment. Peaceful view of the fountain in the pond. Wood-look tile flooring, neutral carpet, stainless steel appliances. Walk in attic space, double pantry and outdoor area with pavers add to this great attached home. With HOA provided law service, it leaves little to be desired.
